{"tid":1313214,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（大膽假設）中聯辦同警察已奪取香港全面控制權","createTime":"2019-07-13T16:56:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T03:42:05.000Z","uid":41458,"like":41,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2bd2bee00c01ee97386310583f3168945da3fd6b","tid":1313214,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T16:56:37.000Z","msg":"純粹大膽假設，歡迎集思廣益<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭係基本上係人質<br />\n所謂保護佢嘅人，其實係殺手<br />\n只要林鄭一亂講嘢就會搞掂佢</span></span><br />\n成個政府都係警察嘅人（滲透多年，經西環用各種方法安插）<br />\n以致警察做任何嘢都冇後果<br />\n宜家即使警察開槍殺人，亦唔會有罪，到時作返一兩個理由就可以<br />\n因為所有制衡到警察嘅人已被全面滲透<br />\n<br />\n相信送中條例當初係西環推，因為佢已經認為冇任何嘢阻到佢地，成個政府控制權係佢手上<br />\n但結果過百萬人上街，政局不穩<br />\n呢隻鑊一定要有人背，最後西環迫林鄭食咗佢<br />\n其他親中界別光速割蓆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（相信609後，林鄭已被要脅要一人承擔所有責任，否則有性命危險）<br />\n表面證據<br />\n1. 林鄭道歉時，全不覺有歉意，甚至令人覺得挑釁. 一來呢隻係死貓，二來，有可能係林鄭刻意，希望借香港人去推翻宜家個政府）<br />\n2. 林鄭再道歉，明顯比第一次好少少，相信畀西環屌咗鑊，要佢呢次做得好好睇。結果作用不大。<br />\n3. 西環幾經辛苦，同警察同成個滲透政府架構，去套取香港控制權，每年可以操控好多千億嘅公帑，有權有錢，當然唔會放手<br />\n4. 林鄭被威脅後，已成為完全嘅傀儡。西環同警察當然唔希望佢下台。咁就算下個上任係親中人士，都要花一番功夫去100％操縱佢<br />\n5. 林鄭最近一次上水，提到自己絕對唔會出賣警察，又話覺得自己生命受到威脅，其實佢係講緊西環同警察。所謂保護佢嘅人，就係隨時可以殺佢嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n其實仲有好多蛛絲馬跡，唔一一盡錄。希望大家一齊補完<br />\n例如<br />\n－曾蔭權事件<br />\n－中央同西環是否兩個派系"},{"pid":"15db4eeec570a0fb7aa89c0de1aa4e14e3320cbe","tid":1313214,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T16:58:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"376cf2da9dabdd3278663e4f6b10246d1b1f34b8","tid":1313214,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T16:58:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f41f9501c10475fa756ff5d71fbb0296871b43a2","tid":1313214,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T17:02:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb85c4a6b67db2aa6fdd7ec12e1a52aa4af83f5","tid":1313214,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T17:08:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc3969b0a7de0c9ce67c87629bf8913fa06e0855","tid":1313214,"uid":35081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T17:12:59.000Z","msg":"林鄭夠膽出聲 我地保護返佢又點話"},{"pid":"d27933fd13718dbcb4de52ccf56c088b630c4dd9","tid":1313214,"uid":35081,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cc3969b0a7de0c9ce67c87629bf8913fa06e0855","tid":1313214,"uid":35081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T17:12:59.000Z","msg":"林鄭夠膽出聲 我地保護返佢又點話"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T17:13:26.000Z","msg":"如果你既假設係真的話"},{"pid":"a354f26ed0c407aeceef2904664a067a92374c8d","tid":1313214,"uid":135274,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T17:17:53.000Z","msg":"提出一點比較少人留意既：<br />\n大家都記得送中暫緩之前爆過幾次走資，但實際係邊啲人呢？<br />\n<br />\n第一個被爆出既係林健鋒<br />\n第二個係梁美芬（實際上係年頭賣咗）<br />\n第三個仲犀利，石禮謙直接call會撻訂，亦係送中二讀前一日<br />\n<br />\n呢三個人有咩特別呢？<strong>同屬經民聯，亦姐係西環係03年之後全力培訓，直屬西環既商家派系</strong><br />\n<br />\n問題黎啦，建制派走資就冇咩好奇怪，但點解爆出黎既全部都係經民聯，而呢件事可以發生三次呢？"},{"pid":"d8fd1480e4522c7ead164898419bab80a0e19d51","tid":1313214,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:31:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fca9027edf26193406bd60c5b62cb47d0c6078ed","tid":1313214,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:32:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74ea3052ae7c9d72a614fbbb325923e179e3f3c2","tid":1313214,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:35:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c5ef01dfb1605e1036dbf7b8795f1fc624a0e74","tid":1313214,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:36:56.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"51e767bba1891527b8121d436d017726fe05e7db","tid":1313214,"uid":279590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:37:06.000Z","msg":"老實講唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"967d0952eb14052b910593207b19e5809b79c686","tid":1313214,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:51:36.000Z","msg":"所見略同 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警隊治港"},{"pid":"fcf1d264dca442e1ab8c05769d08689d32674203","tid":1313214,"uid":233009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:54:00.000Z","msg":"怕"},{"pid":"60ec749ed0e820c667c5fd5f251a49fb52c6cd4e","tid":1313214,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:54:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a68c4020f235fdb29a6cbb17b16a3d1b25d0c51","tid":1313214,"uid":193436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:55:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc5e82332523b79f31516d10b4e60ced65ca53e2","tid":1313214,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cc3969b0a7de0c9ce67c87629bf8913fa06e0855","tid":1313214,"uid":35081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T17:12:59.000Z","msg":"林鄭夠膽出聲 我地保護返佢又點話"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T00:58:25.000Z","msg":"如果樓主推論正確 林鄭落一落區咪搞掂囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢大可以去叫示威者幫佢手清除威脅 <br />\n到時你估班毅進仔同狗官擋得住咩？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而佢無咁做可見樓主諗多左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b67ff899f7dea52d2958013aab8e877d0a3cb90","tid":1313214,"uid":81195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:37:52.000Z","msg":"忍唔住要推！<br />\n結合邏輯同想象力！"},{"pid":"b8b9d3c31ea37e1e90801db2b39deb4f167b027b","tid":1313214,"uid":258340,"like":0,"